dct_description_sm: Surveys of the Imperial Japanese Navy, 1933 & 34 ; [U.S. Hydrographic Office] Emergency Reproduction of Japanese Chart.
Depths shown by soundings, relief by contours and spot heights.
In Japanese, with title and map text also in English.
Year published "昭和11年" taken from bottom margin.
Shows depths, shoals, low water areas, drainage, buildings, roads, coastal vegetation.
